OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after singing
OL,4,Cselfie showed off cannabis farm
OL,6,FA drug dealer who filmed himself
OL,7,Fsinging in a cannabis farm has been
OL,8,Fjailed for five years after his
OL,9,Fsuspicious behaviour led police to a
OL,10,Fdrugs conspiracy.
OL,12,FDetectives began investigating 37-year-
OL,13,Fold Ryan Banham after hundreds of
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds was deposited into
OL,15,Fhis personal bank account.
OL,17,FBanham, of Digby Road, Rochdale, had
OL,18,Fhis home raided and quantities of
OL,19,Fcannabis and cocaine were recovered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
