OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after singing
OL,4,Cselfie showed off cannabis farm
OL,6,FPolice also found a number of mobile
OL,7,Fphones which revealed evidence of drug
OL,8,Ftrafficking, including the supply of
OL,9,Fcannabis, payment discussions, and
OL,10,Fdrug orders.
OL,12,FOne video recovered during the course
OL,13,Fof the investigation revealed Banham
OL,14,Fsinging to the camera while preparing
OL,15,Fdrugs in a cannabis farm.
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Dan Daly from our
OL,18,FRochdale district said: "Banham was
OL,19,Fresponsible for distributing dangerous
OL,20,Fand illicit drugs throughout the
OL,21,FRochdale community and beyond.
