OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after singing
OL,4,Cselfie showed off cannabis farm
OL,6,F"Following an investigation into his
OL,7,Fcriminal dealings, we were able to
OL,8,Fsecure a charge which has led to this
OL,9,Fresult, and ensured a significant
OL,10,Fdisruption to the supply of illegal
OL,11,Fsubstances.
OL,13,F"Across Rochdale, our officers are
OL,14,Fconstantly working to tackle drugs
OL,15,Fsupply and will act on any
OL,16,Fintelligence provided ` which you can
OL,17,Fdo directly or anonymously through
OL,18,FCrimestoppers."
